// NOTE:  FUN
//===========
// Left hand. Function keys
        layer_5 {
            bindings = <
&none      &none             &none           &none           &none             &none                  &kp UP_ARROW           &none            &none          &none          &none         &none            &none
&none      &kp F12           &kp F7          &kp F8          &kp F9            &kp PSCR               &kp DOWN_ARROW         &trans           &trans         &trans         &trans        &trans           &none
&none      &kp F11           &kp F4          &kp F5          &kp F6            &kp SLCK               &kp LEFT_ARROW         &trans           &trans         &trans         &trans        &trans           &none
&none      &kp F10           &kp F1          &kp F2          &kp F3            &kp PAUS               &kp RIGHT_ARROW        &trans           &trans         &trans         &trans        &trans           &none
                                                                                                      &kp C_MUTE      
            &none            &none           &kp APP         &kp SPACE         &kp TAB                &kp ENTER              &trans           &trans         &trans         &none         &none
            >;
